channel.title: WWE's Greatest Moments
channel.desc: Throughout the storied history of WWE, there has never been a Superstar quite as large as the eighth wonder of the world, Andre the Giant. Unforgettable moments of his enormous strength featured in this episode include his showdown with Hulk Hogan at Shea Stadium, the body slam contest with Big John Stud, his triumph at Survivor Series, his extraordinary title win and so much more.
